text: This Is Acting is the seventh studio album by Australian singer-songwriter Sia and was released on 29 January 2016. It topped the album charts in Australia and Norway. It went to the top 10 in Austria, Belgium, Canada, the Czech Republic, Finland, France, Ireland, the Netherlands, New Zealand, Poland, South Korea, Spain, Sweden, Switzerland, the United Kingdom and the United States. == Track listing == == References == Category:2016 albums Category:Sia albums
title: This Is Acting
